<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM4.2.5">
<l>cāṭu pōyviḻat tāḷnimirt tīcaṉṟaṉ paṭaiyoṭuṅ kiḷaiyōṭum</l>
<l>ōṭa vāṇaṉai yāyiran tōḷkaḷun tuṇittava ṉuṟaikōyil</l>
<l>āṭu vāṉkoṭi yakalvicum paṇavi<supplied>p</supplied>pōyp  pakalava ṉoḷimaṟaikkum</l>
<l>māṭa māḷikai cūḻtaru nāṅkūr vaṇpuru ṭōttamamē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The temple where dwells the one who, having [once] stretched out his foot</l>
<l rend="indent">so that a cart went toppling over,</l>
<l>Severed one-thousand arms from Bāṇa so that Īśa’s army and retinue ran,</l>
<l>Is Vaṉpuruṭōttamam in Nānkūr with mansions and palaces</l>
<l rend="indent">encircling effortlessly</l>
<l>Where billowing sky[-high] banners, reaching into the wide heavens,</l>
<l rend="indent">hide the light of the day lord.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
